              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The beryllium targets were prepared in a range of",
                "thicknesses from 10.mu-g/cm2 to 75.mu-g/cm2. These",
                "targets were vacuum evaporated from a tungsten boat.",
                "The thin targets, that is those with thicknesses less",
                "than 30 mu-g/cm2 were evaporated onto 10 mu-g/cm2",
                "carbon foils. The thicker ones were evaporated onto",
                "glass slides and floated off as self-supporting",
                "beryllium foils."
